when the navy and marines were here training I 
talked to him once. I used to have him out as often as

21:28.740 --> 21:32.405
I could before he passed away. Let's go back and 
capture him. Describe him physically and his

21:35.850 --> 21:42.018
manner and style of leadership. Well, he was tall, 
very well-dressed, well-mannered individual,

21:42.238 --> 21:51.791
well-educated man. And he was fairly formal in his 
conduct. with everybody and and really easy to

21:56.635 --> 22:24.651
interpret misinterpret because he was had a 
little bit of a harsh side but he had really a heart

21:56.635 --> 22:24.651
of gold he's one of those people that wanted things 
exactly right but he would anybody's trying he

21:56.635 --> 22:24.651
would support them to the last but if unless it was 
it unless they were violating his opinion and that

21:56.635 --> 22:24.651
would infuriate him greatly And there's some 
instances that some of his other people related to

22:24.968 --> 22:30.976
him, and I could see that as we went along. But if he 
thought he could do something for you, he would do

