25:01.497 --> 25:08.784
breakdown of quality control and people get sick? 
And did we ever have an outbreak of anything? We

25:11.728 --> 25:16.793
didn't have any big outbreaks, but we, we had a, we 
had a few where, where, uh, But nothing was ever

25:17.380 --> 25:23.909
identified as having caused it. And what I did, 
when we suspected something, I'd get the food

25:23.949 --> 25:39.851
sanitarium here on campus to look at it and arrange 
for any tests that needed to be done. So we

25:40.812 --> 25:43.135
precluded most of that. Actually, there's seldom 
really any chance for that if your sanitation is

25:43.469 --> 25:50.678
good enough. Now, I know there's always a chance 
for anything, but we were very blessed to not have

25:50.698 --> 26:00.730
any serious things developed. Let's make believe 
there's going to be a big dinner on Saturday. The

26:08.040 --> 26:09.241
president's going to host it. We've got a number of 
dignitaries coming. who would select the menu and

26:11.903 --> 26:17.749
how far in advance would you need to start planning 
it? Well, of course, we would coordinate with the,

26:19.130 --> 26:32.264
or vice versa, with the president's secretary or 
assistant to work out the basic menu. If it's a

26:32.284 --> 26:34.606
buffet, we had free reign. But if it's a seated 
affair, it would be different. So that would

26:38.785 --> 26:45.071
usually happen and should happen maybe a week or 
two in advance, just traditionally. Not

26:45.171 --> 26:46.272
necessarily so. We could do that within 48 hours 
easy enough. But was it routine only a week in

26:49.976 --> 26:55.682
advance for you and your staff to sit down? About 
that. That was sort of routine, not essential. But

26:59.806 --> 27:08.775
we would have an idea about the number, and we would 
